TopLevelNameStatus Enum

Definition

Indicates the forest trust account status of a top-level domain in a forest.

In this Article

public enum TopLevelNameStatus
Inheritance
Object
ValueType
System.Enum
TopLevelNameStatus

Fields

AdminDisabled

The forest trust account is disabled by administrative action.
ConflictDisabled

The forest trust account is disabled due to a conflict with an existing forest trust account.
Enabled

The forest trust account is enabled.
NewlyCreated

The forest trust account was disabled on creation.
